        "content": "<p>If you have an unclosed comment in your file, the error messages are not great:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">Nat.add</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- type mismatch</span>\n<span class=\"c\">/-</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>or</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">Nat.add</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- type mismatch</span>\n<span class=\"k\">#exit</span>\n<span class=\"c\">/-</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Note:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">Nat</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">Nat.add</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- fine</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
